</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d240n1-ptr" id="PJA11d240n1">1</a>

   <p>Memorial to the States General, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0129" class="document">8 March</a>, above.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d240n2-ptr" id="PJA11d240n2">2</a>

   <p>From the Duc de La Vauguyon, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0198-0002" class="document">17 April</a>, above.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d240n3-ptr" id="PJA11d240n3">3</a>

   <p>From Dumas, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0193-0002" class="document">14 April</a>, above.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d240n4-ptr" id="PJA11d240n4">4</a>

   <p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Charles Adams (17701800), son of John and Abigail Adams ]">CA</abbr>.</p>

